<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 40px 20px;">
  <div style="max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; padding: 32px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">

    <h1 style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; color: #111827;">
      WineHub – Reset Password
    </h1>

    <p style="color: #374151; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 18px;">
      Hello <strong><%= @resource.email %></strong>,
    </p>

    <p style="color: #374151; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 22px;">
      Someone requested a link to change your WineHub password. If this was you, click the button below.
    </p>

    <p style="margin: 0 0 22px 0;">
      <%= link_to "Change my password",
                  edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token),
                  style: "display:inline-block; background:#2563eb; color:#ffffff; text-decoration:none; font-weight:600; padding:12px 18px; border-radius:10px;" %>
    </p>

    <div style="background: #f3f4f6; padding: 16px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 18px 0 22px 0;">
      <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #374151;">
        If you didn’t request this, you can safely ignore this email.
      </p>
      <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px; color: #374151;">
        Your password won’t change until you open the link and set a new one.
      </p>
    </div>

    <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; margin: 0 0 6px 0;">
      Button not working? Copy and paste this link into your browser:
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #111827; word-break: break-all; margin: 0 0 22px 0;">
      <%= edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token) %>
    </p>

    <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; margin: 24px 0;">

    <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; text-align: center; margin: 0;">
      © <%= Time.current.year %> WineHub
    </p>

  </div>
</div>